# ============================================================
# JUPYTER NOTEBOOK SHORTCUTS CHEAT SHEET
# ============================================================

# -------------------------
# COMMAND MODE (Press Esc)
# -------------------------
# A           -> Insert cell Above
# B           -> Insert cell Below
# D, D        -> Delete selected cell
# X           -> Cut cell
# C           -> Copy cell
# V           -> Paste cell below
# Shift + V   -> Paste cell above
# Z           -> Undo deleted cell
# M           -> Convert cell to Markdown
# Y           -> Convert cell to Code
# R           -> Convert cell to Raw
# Enter       -> Enter Edit mode
# H           -> Show all shortcuts
# O           -> Toggle cell output
# Shift + O   -> Toggle output scrolling
# L           -> Toggle line numbers
# Shift + L   -> Toggle line numbers for all cells
# I, I        -> Interrupt kernel
# 0, 0        -> Restart kernel
# Shift + M   -> Merge selected cells
# S           -> Save notebook

# -------------------------
# EDIT MODE (Press Enter)
# -------------------------
# Shift + Enter -> Run cell and move to next
# Ctrl + Enter  -> Run cell and stay in current cell
# Alt + Enter   -> Run cell and insert new cell below
# Tab           -> Autocomplete
# Shift + Tab   -> Show documentation tooltip
# Ctrl + /      -> Comment/Uncomment selected lines
# Ctrl + Z      -> Undo
# Ctrl + Y      -> Redo
# Ctrl + A      -> Select all text
# Ctrl + C      -> Copy
# Ctrl + X      -> Cut
# Ctrl + V      -> Paste
# Ctrl + Shift + - -> Split cell at cursor

# -------------------------
# NAVIGATION
# -------------------------
# Up Arrow      -> Move to previous cell
# Down Arrow    -> Move to next cell
# Home          -> Go to beginning of line
# End           -> Go to end of line
# Page Up       -> Scroll up
# Page Down     -> Scroll down

# -------------------------
# USEFUL JUPYTER MAGICS
# -------------------------
# %pwd          -> Show current working directory
# %ls           -> List files
# %who          -> List variables
# %whos         -> Detailed variable information
# %reset        -> Clear variables
# %time         -> Time a single execution
# %timeit       -> Benchmark execution speed
# %history      -> Show command history
# %run file.py  -> Run a Python script
# %matplotlib inline -> Show plots inside notebook

# -------------------------
# HELP COMMANDS
# -------------------------
# ?function_name    -> Quick help
# ??function_name   -> Detailed help/source
# help(function)    -> Python help

# -------------------------
# KERNEL SHORTCUTS
# -------------------------
# I, I         -> Interrupt kernel
# 0, 0         -> Restart kernel
# Esc + H      -> View all available shortcuts

# ============================================================
# Most Important Daily Shortcuts:
# Shift + Enter  -> Run cell
# Alt + Enter    -> Run + New Cell
# A              -> New cell above
# B              -> New cell below
# D,D            -> Delete cell
# M              -> Markdown cell
# Y              -> Code cell
# Tab            -> Autocomplete
# Shift + Tab    -> Documentation
# Ctrl + /       -> Comment code
# ============================================================